{"type":"message","id":"7ba2d2fd","parentId":"7a00577b","timestamp":"2026-03-31T22:41:39.034Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering trusted sources**\n\nI’m thinking about how we might quickly check if there’s a list of trusted paths we can follow. It could include manual sources, which might help ensure we’re on the right track. I want to make sure I’m considering all options available to provide the user with accurate information. Exploring these trusted sources together could be beneficial!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_077585180826814c0169cc4d9bf490819a87cc9b53f379f58b\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpzE2i8LmkoLF-4sm_aGicceAEgYrHwHmf042Nu9uu6q6B17RXoAwZidIdfvWSL4f6ddvDMRebpXB6KDhpkyRngU8wrS2I0ZfKZqQ8fmfaqvObJbZSYBzplqOcDLKe2IgNeOdSaZKlQEJDmg0m_j45q0zHBRpRK0GPeLxxyqB_DfNWbYYh9X2b5gkmZrzyzzqobDMe1sApgyAj5NPnl8cXGDg4hB9Xas4Z50QRhkLiflkjV4jI-zg69iOw4KWxtGkNFTpkf5iCn_L4Ma_EdWT-vB26sNDGhyIfqoCNvxgJfhIFMvRF_xJ9JHBzRzoL8RcFeDWrb5Dg8STKxdS0_Gvl4ub5TiEM3ZfSSPa7six0oOOVQED92VflntcYagJ6Nu1Dl9baKyRwTPFSTCs-t7zD4GBf26u9a6kCLzHv2WTm8jn8jQf9teJPeP2sqkiDwmjvzUkSqTuxV5bSV3vUaYHHzgloPYZrjZuhGi4uNpZ6mgNHfCGBJvJNFE0yngzZWV3o8kEH1g3IFYeAhKATb9fi3JmRd7DWkAb8llsgs89FNXuEnWMvu8W9e1weBcUttPfc33MaGrYXRAamBkM4ww3ErvgU3U7PTzFIAUelMhbvT_AB1JNZSnD77beffDZUE_nCExaPOwL2E4i20ZbhRZbLwd07kQR4RkWiVpiGO-qGwi2jbEsS3DGtgYm4TdijN5dkUoVYMQjeaugnjo5ErtG0kvRZUUOeu8WDCVBkn4fFIWaISHWlRlcdYnxaAbaJL6wYqLeCSXjnDKJiUcTuGUo2wlPFgauoyuICFLh6gSIv3v1EnK9o7tjqOSfOXy96epX5Ep3z0C2NLQVaK_7HNb6M0NQmlMh2PE6Cs-b7YtpL0uNk1qoOO5LYgC6ACQDzMF7jMJRAmVUWFRSx0DAnP6ScJ1QisS10fSOvcMryBbo2_-wiWhKB0rheCaLKFHTb-tgrvgR2lwF_XbxxX4k5gBZ6861vLukA7H55ZQ_GIXrbw1YPLFRFPOmKQnC-50PS34eFj0ds6z6w9sHi6dfNjDXf17dkkB__Bxo3A0IDtIq8347tC03-D4MdN8XLn_Vv1iuYNrKEBG-b6tMFIezsBoQ1jrQbJF3CXAhucVjgLilgH_h3qCkRJWMXHPxezGDcitJDFL99yyZUhuWe1qyvky5Mkt5mcRCPs3uWM2s_PBEp8R32FAHtk4XU6FiVQ4lQ7ifpevg29nyfKjujDrvbEfdNAdzLQwkQC0sZnMf0mKH8BcEplsL7DlAmcfPSxOo5JcyXj9fIdfoV3-G-qDmHGdFyfNEltXsP4