{"type":"message","id":"d892bbf0","parentId":"42a9a48a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T02:05:29.588Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (张玲) is asking why the buy candidates don't have recommended buy prices. This is a good question. Looking at the intelligence brief output, it shows candidates with scores and weights but no buy prices.\n\nLet me think about what the current system actually outputs:\n- The candidates have scores (评分) and weights (权重)\n- But no \"可执行买价\" (executable buy price)\n\nAccording to Zhang Ling's USER.md:\n- 非交易日 / 非交易时段不要给\"可执行买价\"；只给预算、标的和开盘触发条件\n- But it's 10:05 AM on a trading day, so the market is open\n\n\n- The system appears to be generating buy signals but stopping there without providing entry prices, which is a gap in the current output","thinkingSignature":"6e49f4da0ae97351a61d7c65801c21c2490e5e614b6423646f206cffe820c401"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 问得好，这是当前链路的一个缺口。\n\n**现状是：**\n- 候选输出 → `评分` + `权重`\n- 没有 → `可执行买价`\n\n**原因有两层：**\n\n1. **简报层**：`intelligence_brief` 只聚合评分和权重，没接买入价格触发逻辑\n2. **执行卡层**：`daily_exec_card` 有价格，但那是对已核候选的复核，不是从简报直出的\n\n**现在盘中，我可以给你补上：**\n针对 `002342.SZ` / `002471.SZ` / `002361.SZ` 这三只，从今日实时行情里抓一个参考买价（不构成投资建议，仅供参考）。\n\n要我现在出吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":88,"output":320,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":99321,"totalTokens":99729,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775009105270,"responseId":"061bb051ae33b452a31fe4884b340c7f"}}
