{"type":"message","id":"0a15a9dc","parentId":"cb8fe989","timestamp":"2026-04-01T07:42:49.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"张玲说她在今天（0401）加了500股诺思格（301333.SZ），她让我在16:10去获取最新的持仓信息。\n\n现在的时间是15:42，她说让我在16:10去获取。\n\n我有两个选择：\n1. 立刻去获取（现在15:42已经接近16:10了）\n2. 设一个定时任务在16:10执行\n\n考虑到她明确说了\"四点十分\"，我应该设一个定时任务到时候去抓持仓。\n\n但实际上，我可以先立刻抓一次当前的持仓（因为16:10还没到，但现在已经15:42很接近了），同时也可以考虑设一个16:10的定时任务。\n\n\n她的指令很明确，所以我需要设置一个定时提醒在16:10执行，这样到时候才能真正获取到最新的持仓变化。","thinkingSignature":"37f084e25217660624e73ecf3e7eaa303bb61f6adc66daf2a3fe777db109ce93"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 收到，我设好16:10的定时获取，到时候自动去抓你最新的诺思格加仓后的持仓快照。\n\n现在先立刻抓一次当前最新状态做基准。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7cg789rj47qb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace && python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport csv, json\np = Path('quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/account_holdings_selected_latest.csv')\nif p.exists():\n    rows = list(csv.DictReader(p.open(encoding='utf-8-sig')))\n    target = [r for r in rows if '301333' in (r.get('symbol') or r.get('ts_code') or '')]\n    print(f'当前持仓文件: {len(rows)}只')\n    for t in target:\n        print(f\"  {t}\")\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":20}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7cg789rj47qb_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace && python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom datetime import datetime\nprint(f'当前时间: {datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")}')\n# 16:10 = 28分钟后\nfrom datetime import timedelta\ntarget = datetime.now().replace(hour=16, minute=10, second=0)\nnow = datetime.now()\nif target <= now:\n    target += timedelta(days=1)\ndelta = (target - now).total_seconds()\nprint(f'距离16:10还有 {int(delta//60)} 分 {int(delta%60)} 秒')\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"ou