{"type":"message","id":"4712971f","parentId":"2b461511","timestamp":"2026-04-01T07:43:21.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the current holdings file shows 301333.SZ诺思格 with 400 shares at cost 77.632. The user said she added 500 shares today. So the new total should be 900 shares.\n\nThe current time is 15:42, and I need to set a task for 16:10. That's 27 minutes and 10 seconds from now. I'll create a deferred task using a background exec with sleep.\n\nLet me create a task that:\n1. Sleeps until 16:10\n2. Reads the current holdings (using ths web scraping or whatever the current source is)\n3. Reports to this group chat\n\nI should not just \"reply\" here but I should use the message tool to send to this group chat when done. Actually, I'll use exec with sleep and then use the feishu_doc or exec to fetch and then message.\n\n\nI'll set up a background exec that waits until 16:10, then pulls the latest holdings via the THS web scraping tool and posts the results to the Feishu group. Since the user's holdings file still shows 400 shares, I need to fetch the actual updated position at that time.\n\nWriting the background script...","thinkingSignature":"c4fce6b31fe704f3bc656cd2454739eefa337781c25443dc0c1d3345b8e9e32c"},{"type":"text","text":"当前基准：诺思格 = **400股**，离16:10还有约27分钟。我设好定时触发，到时候去抓THS实盘持仓并推送。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cbvckbazfh9b_1","name":"write","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/run_logs/task_fetch_holdings_1610.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"16:10 持仓快照获取任务\"\"\"\nimport sys\nimport time\nimport subprocess\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nLOG = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/run_logs/fetch_holdings_1610.log')\nLOG.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n\ndef log(msg):\n    ts = datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n    line = f'[{ts}] {msg}'\n    print(line, flush=True)\n    with LOG.open('a', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        f.write(line + '\\n')\n\nlog('16:10持仓获取任务启动')\n\n# 等待到16:10\nnow = datetime.now()\ntarget = now.replace(hour=16, minute=10, second=0, microsecond=0)\nif target <= now:\n    from datetime import timedelta\n    target += timedelta(days=1)\nwait_sec = (target - now).total_seconds()\nlog(f'等待 {int(wait_sec//60)} 分 {int(wait_sec%60)} 秒，目标是 {target}')\ntime.sleep(max(0, wait_sec))\n\n# 再次确认时间\nlog(f'触发时间确认: {datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")}')\n\n# 运行THS本地持仓同步（抓最新）\nscripts = [\n    # 优先用THS web抓最新持仓\n    'python3 -c \"from pathlib import Path; import subprocess; r = subprocess.run([\\\"python3\\\", \\\"scripts/sync_selected_real_holdings.py\\\"], capture_output=True, text=True); print(r.stdout[-2000:] if r.stdout else r.stderr[-2000:] if r.stderr else \\'no output\\')\"',\n]\nresult_lines = ['']\nfor cmd in scripts:\n    try:\n        r = subprocess.run(cmd, shell=True, capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=60)\n        out = (r.stdout + r.stderr)[-1000:]\n        result_lines.append(f'CMD: {cmd[:80]}')\n        result_lines.append(f'OUT: {out}')\n    except Exception as e:\n        result_lines.append(f'ERROR: {e}')\n\n# 读最新持仓文件\np = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/account_holdings_selected_latest.csv')\nlines_out = []\nif p.exists():\n    import csv\n    rows = list(csv.DictReader(p.open(encoding='utf-8-sig')))\n    target = [r for r in rows if '301333' in (r.get('symbol') or r.get('ts_code') or '')]\n    lines_out.append(f'持仓文件共{len(rows)}只，诺思格={target}')\n    for r in rows:\n        lines_out.append(f\"  {r.get('ts_code','')} {r.get('name','')} qty={r.get('qty','')} cost={r.get('cost_price','')}\")\nelse:\n    lines_out.append('持仓文件不存在')\n\nreport = '\\n'.join(result_lines + [''] + lines_out)\nLOG.write_text(report, encoding='utf-8')\nlog(f'获取完成，结果:\\n{report[:3000]}')\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":81137,"output":1039,"cacheRead":25551,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107727,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775029369116,"responseId":"061bff7969bc13063f608dc99322d3a6"}}
