{"type":"message","id":"fb5e3b9a","parentId":"603969ad","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:25:56.622Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the actual current THS local holdings. There are 3 ledgers in the THS list, and the system's current selected holdings is `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.csv` which only has 23 stocks and still shows 诺思格 as 400 shares.\n\nThe THS skill's `list` command shows what the actual THS local files have. The ledger `2269916_10276930` has 36 stocks and includes 301333.SZ among others. But the currently selected source (`ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.csv`) was exported from the web source (tzzb.10jqka.com.cn) and doesn't include the new 500 shares.\n \nI need to sync the THS local holdings using those ledger IDs so the system reflects the actual 36-stock portfolio with the updated share count, rather than relying on the stale web-sourced file.","thinkingSignature":"6df5e8c827c84dd938154438bcdfd1337b9d48829e662b9386f231768abd7bf9"},{"type":"text","text":"找到根因了——THS skill 已经能读到本地 App 的 3 个账户，但系统的 `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.csv` 还是旧的口径（23只，诺思格400股）。\n\n我现在直接用 THS 账户重建物化 selected 文件，把你那 500 股诺思格接进去。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hmw307o6k4hs_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport csv, json, subprocess, tempfile\n\nPYTHON = 'python3'\nskill_script = Path.home() / '.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_local_holdings.py'\nBASE = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system')\nOUT_DIR = BASE / 'research/reports'\nSELECTED_CONFIG = BASE / 'config/ths_local_holdings_selection.json'\n\n# 方案：用 THS 本地 ledger 2269916_10276930（有36只持仓的那个）来导出\n# 先检查 selection config 里有没有 ledger 配置\ncfg = {}\nif SELECTED_CONFIG.exists():\n    cfg = json.loads(SELECTED_CONFIG.read_text(encoding='utf-8'))\n    print('selection_config:', json.dumps(cfg, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)[:1000])\n\n# 直接用 THS local holdings 的 list 结果里最大的那个 ledger 导出\n# ledger_ids = ['2269916', '10276930'] - 这个账户有 36 只持仓\nledger_ids = ['2269916', '10276930']\n\nwith tempfile.TemporaryDirectory() as tmpdir:\n    # 构造临时 selection config\n    tmp_cfg = Path(tmpdir) / 'selection.json'\n    tmp_cfg.write_text(json.dumps({\n        'enabled': True,\n        'selected_ledger_ids': ledger_ids\n    }, ensure_ascii=False), encoding='utf-8')\n    \n    r = subprocess.run(\n        [PYTHON, str(skill_script), 'export',\n         '--selection-config', str(tmp_cfg),\n         '--out-dir', tmpdir,\n         '--csv-name', 'ths_local_latest.csv',\n         '--json-name', 'ths_local_latest.json'],\n        capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=60\n    )\n    print('export returncode:', r.returncode)\n    print('stdout:', r.stdout[:2000])\n    print('stderr:', r.stderr[:500] if r.stderr else '')\n    \n    tmp = Path(tmpdir)\n    for f in tmp.glob('*'):\n        print(f'  导出文件: {f.name} size={f.stat().st_size}')\n        content = f.read_text(encoding='utf-8')[:2000]\n        print(content[:1000])\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":90}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":87932,"output":796,"cacheRead":25551,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114279,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775031926580,"responseId":"061c09781f4ea922e65668b36dc86745"}}
