{"type":"message","id":"57a8375e","parentId":"b5d454b8","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:26:22.342Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - the THS local holdings export returned 63 holdings (combining all 3 ledgers). But 63 is too many. The user said they had about 23 A-stock holdings + some others. But the combined three ledgers give 63 total.\n\nI need to find the specific ledger that has the 诺思格 with 900 shares (400 + 500 new purchase). Looking at the ledger list:\n- `XcsLscjDataFile_2269916_10276930` has 36 symbols and includes 301333.SZ\n\nLet me check the quantity for 301333.SZ in that ledger specifically. \n\nNow I'm extracting the actual holdings data from the CSV file for ledger 2269916 to see what 301333.SZ shows there.","thinkingSignature":"11e1e5630b139cf533cf7b7373b7319e374f336ff95a5816f6213f6815690ad0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ramih8caexmq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport csv, subprocess, tempfile, json\n\nPYTHON = 'python3'\nskill_script = Path.home() / '.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_local_holdings.py'\nBASE = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system')\n\n# 只用 ledger 2269916（包含诺思格的那个账户）\nwith tempfile.TemporaryDirectory() as tmpdir:\n    tmp_cfg = Path(tmpdir) / 'selection.json'\n    tmp_cfg.write_text(json.dumps({\n        'enabled': True,\n        'selected_ledger_ids': ['2269916', '10276930']\n    }, ensure_ascii=False), encoding='utf-8')\n    \n    r = subprocess.run(\n        [PYTHON, str(skill_script), 'export',\n         '--selection-config', str(tmp_cfg),\n         '--out-dir', tmpdir,\n         '--csv-name', 'ths_local_2269916.csv',\n         '--json-name', 'ths_local_2269916.json'],\n        capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=60\n    )\n    tmp = Path(tmpdir)\n    \n    # 找诺思格\n    for f in tmp.glob('*.csv'):\n        if 'ths_local' in f.name:\n            rows = list(csv.DictReader(f.open(encoding='utf-8')))\n            target = [r for r in rows if '301333' in str(r)]\n            print(f'{f.name}: {len(rows)}行')\n            for t in target:\n                print(f'  诺思格: {dict(t)}')\n            # 也检查哪些有数量\n            for r in rows:\n                sym = r.get('symbol','')\n                qty = r.get('quantity','')\n                cost = r.get('cost_price','')\n                name = r.get('name','')\n                if sym:\n                    print(f\"  {sym} {name} qty={qty} cost={cost}\")\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90325,"output":640,"cacheRead":25551,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116516,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775031956819,"responseId":"061c099532564d6551088cffcf00a38c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0cd302c4","parentId":"57a8375e","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:26:22.533Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ramih8caexmq_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ths_local_2269916.csv: 63行\n  诺思格: {'\\ufeffsymbol': '301333.SZ', 'asset_type': 'stock', 'name': '', 'quantity': '400', 'cost_price': '77.625000', 'source_path': '/Users/ling/Library/Containers/cn.com.10jqka.macstockPro/Data/Documents/XcsFold/XcsLscjDataFile_2269916_10276930', 'ledger_ids': '2269916|10276930'}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":144,"aggregated":"ths_local_2269916.csv: 63行\n  诺思格: {'\\ufeffsymbol': '301333.SZ', 'asset_type': 'stock', 'name': '', 'quantity': '400', 'cost_price': '77.625000', 'source_path': '/Users/ling/Library/Containers/cn.com.10jqka.macstockPro/Data/Documents/XcsFold/XcsLscjDataFile_2269916_10276930', 'ledger_ids': '2269916|10276930'}","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775031982528}}
{"type":"message","id":"538d2c45","parentId":"0cd302c4","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:27:05.332Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Even the THS local ledger `2269916` still shows 400 shares of 诺思格, not 900. This means the local ledger file on disk hasn't been updated with today's new 500-share purchase.\n\nThe issue is that the THS Mac app has a local data file that hasn't been refreshed with today's trade. The `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.csv` (from tzzb.10jqka.com.cn) is what the system is using, but it also shows 400 shares.\n\nHowever, the user confirmed that the new 500 shares of 诺思格 have been bought and settled. The system just doesn't have the updated data because:\n\n\n1. The THS Mac app's local data files haven't been updated yet, OR\n2. The web tzzb source hasn't been refreshed\n\nSince the user explicitly said the shares were bought and already settled, I need to manually update the holdings CSV to reflect the new position. I'll add 500 shares to the existing 400 shares at the same cost basis to get 900 total shares, then update the system and relevant reports accordingly.\n\nThe user's note about \"加了500股诺思格\" suggests they bought 500 additional shares rather than bought 500 total, so I should combine these positions to get the actual 900-share holding. Since the system still shows 400 shares and can't be automatically refreshed, I'll manually update the CSV file with this corrected position and then notify the user.","thinkingSignature":"9c9178baa65950bf5c122c487321bb0eb5df1e63faaa50774e31b4266ebb392a"},{"type":"text","text":"查到了——THS App 本地账本文件里诺思格还是 400 股，今天新加的 500 股还没被 App 同步到本地文件。\n\n我现在直接把持仓文件里的诺思格手动更新成你确认的 900 股，然后重生物化 selected 文件。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_o6ttpqaukz7e_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport csv, json, shutil\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nBASE = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system')\nREPORTS = BASE / 'research/reports'\nWS_REPORTS = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports')\n\n# 读取当前 selected 文件\np = REPORTS / 'ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.csv'\nrows = list(csv.DictReader(p.open(encoding='utf-8-sig')))\nprint(f'更新前: {len(rows)}行')\ntarget = [r for r in rows if '301333' in str(r)]\nprint(f'诺思格更新前: {target}')\n\nupdated = False\nfor r in rows:\n    if (r.get('symbol') or '').strip() == '301333.SZ':\n        old_qty = r.get('quantity', '400')\n        r['quantity'] = '900'  # 400 + 500 新购入\n        r['cost_price'] = '77.632'  # 保持原成本\n        print(f'诺思格更新: {old_qty} -> 900股')\n        updated = True\n\nif updated:\n    # 写回文件\n    date_tag = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n    \n    # 1. ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.csv\n    p.write_text('', encoding='utf-8')\n    with p.open('w', newline='', encoding='utf-8-sig') as f:\n        writer = csv.DictWriter(f, fieldnames=['symbol','asset_type','name','quantity','cost_price','source_path','ledger_ids'])\n        writer.writeheader()\n        writer.writerows(rows)\n    \n    # 2. ths_web_selected_holdings_YYYYMMDD.csv\n    dated_p = REPORTS / f'ths_web_selected_holdings_{date_tag}.csv'\n    dated_p.write_text('', encoding='utf-8')\n    with dated_p.open('w', newline='', encoding='utf-8-sig') as f:\n        writer = csv.DictWriter(f, fieldnames=['symbol','asset_type','name','quantity','cost_price','source_path','ledger_ids'])\n        writer.writeheader()\n        writer.writerows(rows)\n    \n    # 3. account_holdings_selected_latest.csv（标准化格式）\n    acc = REPORTS / 'account_holdings_selected_latest.csv'\n    compat_rows = []\n    for r in rows:\n        sym = (r.get('symbol') or '').strip()\n        if not sym:\n            continue\n        compat_rows.append({\n            'ts_code': sym,\n            'qty': str(r.get('quantity', '')),\n            'name': str(r.get('name', '')),\n            'cost_price': str(r.get('cost_price', '')),\n            'currency': 'CNY' if sym.endswith(('.SZ','.SH')) else ('HKD' if sym.endswith('.HK') else 'CNY'),\n            'asset_type': str(r.get('asset_type', 'stock'))\n        })\n    acc.write_text('', encoding='utf-8')\n    with acc.open('w', newline='', encoding='utf-8-sig') as f:\n        writer = csv.DictWriter(f, fieldnames=['ts_code','qty','name','cost_price','currency','asset_type'])\n        writer.writeheader()\n        writer.writerows(compat_rows)\n    \n    # 同步到 workspace reports\n    for src in [p, dated_p, acc]:\n        dst = WS_REPORTS / src.name\n        dst.write_bytes(src.read_bytes())\n    \n    # 4. selected_real_holdings_source_latest.json\n    meta = {\n        'generated_at': datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'),\n        'source_reason': 'web_selected_latest_updated_with_user_confirmed_trade',\n        'note': '诺思格300333.SZ已由用户张玲确认加仓500股，总量更新为900股',\n        'holding_count': len(compat_rows),\n        'selected_files': [str(p)],\n    }\n    meta_path = REPORTS / 'selected_real_holdings_source_latest.json'\n    meta_path.write_text(json.dumps(meta, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding='utf-8')\n    (WS_REPORTS / meta_path.name).write_text(json.dumps(meta, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding='utf-8')\n    \n    print(f'\\n更新完成!')\n    print(f'总持仓: {len(rows)}行')\n    print(f'诺思格: 900股')\n    \n    # 验证\n    acc_rows = list(csv.DictReader(WS_REPORTS / 'account_holdings_selected_latest.csv'.open(encoding='utf-8-sig')))\n    t = [r for r in acc_rows if '301333' in str(r)]\n    print(f'验证: {t}')\nelse:\n    print('未找到诺思格')\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":91096,"output":1493,"cacheRead":25551,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118140,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775031982534,"responseId":"061c09ae035cd13cfc89f1fcea8e386a"}}
