{"type":"message","id":"53622d01","parentId":"5251620b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:27:24.061Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The update is confirmed. 诺思格 is now 900 shares in both the quant project reports directory and the workspace reports directory.\n\nNow I need to report back to the user:\n1. The system's THS App data hasn't synced the new 500 shares yet (local files still show 400)\n2. I've manually updated the holdings files to reflect the confirmed 900 shares\n3. The update is done in both places\n\nLet me give a clear summary reply.","thinkingSignature":"2ee4eac0073705a71633dcc45ed0e73168af9105e9255c9d336b681ea94fc4cd"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 查清楚了，也有结论了。\n\n**系统现状：**\n- THS App 本地文件**还没同步到**今天新买的 500 股（本地账本里诺思格还是 400 股）\n- 这是 App 数据刷新的事，系统端控制不了\n\n**我已经做的：**\n- 根据你说的\"加了 500 股且已成交\"，把系统持仓文件直接更新为 **900 股**\n- `account_holdings_selected_latest.csv` 里诺思格现在是 `900 股 @ 77.632`\n- 两份同步文件（quant项目目录 + workspace目录）都已更新\n\n**附注：**\n- THS App 本地文件没有自动更新，所以系统里没有这笔新买的来源记录\n- 如果你希望系统以后能自动抓到这类盘中成交，需要同花顺 App 那边先把本地数据刷新一下"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":93160,"output":277,"cacheRead":25551,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118988,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775032033436,"responseId":"061c09e1dccc6fb43762f0dddc946b6d"}}
