{"type":"message","id":"63674fc0","parentId":"165b2b25","timestamp":"2026-04-01T08:56:04.929Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is confirming:\n1. 诺思格 (301333.SZ) 今天买入500股，成本价每股67.58元\n2. Total should be 900股 (400 existing + 500 new)\n\nI need to calculate the blended cost:\n- Old: 400股 @ 77.632\n- New: 500股 @ 67.58\n- Total cost = (400 × 77.632 + 500 × 67.58) / 900 = (31,052.8 + 33,790) / 900 = 64,842.8 / 900 = 72.047... ≈ 72.05\n\n\n- \nNow I'm verifying the blended cost calculation comes to approximately 72.05元 per share, then I'll update the holding records and ask the user to confirm before making the change.","thinkingSignature":"3813a2af073ff8b4dea531712150aed279990b3948b27bbbd111f0a29414d997"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，这涉及到成本计算，我先把新成本算出来给你确认。\n\n**诺思格加权成本计算：**\n- 原有：400股 @ 77.632元\n- 新买：500股 @ 67.58元\n- 合计：900股\n- **加权成本 = (400×77.632 + 500×67.58) ÷ 900 = 72.05元/股**\n\n今日盈亏会变成：**最新价71.63 vs 成本72.05 → 亏损约0.58%**\n\n系统更新为：诺思格 **900股 @ 72.05元**，确认吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":312,"cacheRead":132463,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132849,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775033749159,"responseId":"061c1095e2b8f3156484f2bc88d88209"}}
