message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Excellent! The script works perfectly! It fetched weibo from 9 KOLs and produced a clean report. Now let me set up a cron job to run this twice daily and send results to Feishu.\\n\\nNow I need to:\\n1. Set up the cron job (twice daily: 08:30 and 20:30)\\n2. Make it send to Feishu after generating the report\\n\\nFor Feishu, I can use the `message` tool to send to the group chat. Let me update the script to also send to Feishu.\\n\\nActually, looking at the system prompt, I can use the `message` tool directly without any special MCP. Let me update the script to send to Feishu.\\n\\n\\nThe report is already well-structured, so I'll just finalize the cron setup and confirm everything's working.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"03b14df6a442737459af5cf200e86dc4dec9063eb7e7b41278652460f03ddbd6\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"🎉 **完美运行！** 9位大V，17条财经内容，全部抓到了！\\n\\n报告内容非常丰富：\\n- 洪榕警告\\\"不要杀跌\\\"（970赞）\\n- wu2198 判断大盘调整（11038赞！）\\n- 马靖昊分析佰维存储年报\\n- 投行泰山发现国家队ETF买入信号\\n\\n现在来设置**每天两次定时推送**：\\n\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_function_vd434jmxquqo_1\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"crontab -l 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"no crontab\\\"\"}}],\"api\":\"anthropic-messages\",\"provider\":\"minimax-portal\",\"model\":\"MiniMax-M2.7\",\"usage\":{\"input\":77111,\"output\":298,\"cacheRead\":33079,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":110488,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1774254480842}}\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/agents/coding-agent/sessions/f997b97d-137e-4f54-8c46-e791945a9ae5.jsonl.reset.2026-03-24T05-40-46.609Z:428:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e35a987a\",\"parentId\":\"3cc37c03\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-23T08:55:59.562Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The data is great! Now I need to push this to Feishu. Let me use the cron_weibo_monitor.py script to send to Feishu. Actually, let me just send the message directly via openclaw.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"aa58cf719f79f70acd53d1ed09bca1d4ddba5aa79cdd5e322acb2d014af6af63\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"数据很丰富，现在推送到飞书：\\n\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_function_pqj5wyfh360t_1\",\"name\":\"exec\",\"arguments\":{\"command\":\"/Users/ling/.local/share/fnm/aliases/default/bin/openclaw message send --channel feishu --target \\\"chat:oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\\\" -m \\\"\\n📊 **微博财经大V每日简报**\\n🕐 2026-03-23 16:55  |  共 10 位大V  |  财经内容 19 条\\n\\n── 重点内容摘录 ──\\n\\n**🔹 洪榕**（职业投资人）\\n   14:17 不要杀跌了，看看今晚美股的底牌。\\n   👍991 💬169 🔁16\\n   15:14 做个股评：今晚美股杀跌，后面华尔街出手止战。 A股借这次战事让投资者彻底放低预期，自此A股不再急涨急跌。皆大欢喜。\\n   👍861 💬135 🔁40\\n\\n**🔹 wu2198**（投资内容创作者）\\n   15:05 今天大盘延续上周的调整趋势进一步扩大空间，盘中下试了3794点，收在3813.28点；按技术面看4190和4197构筑双头之后所形成的IV浪调整还在持续，要等做的话需要耐心等待2026年的\\\"干\\\"字出现才相对安全些。 收到请回复666或点赞支持一下！\\n   👍12376 💬1333 🔁104\\n   14:46 伦敦金自5598.75美元的下跌，第一步起码在4000美元。然后才是3500美元。\\n   👍7216 💬355 🔁75\\n\\n**🔹 唐史主任司马迁**（职业投资人）\\n   08:22 周指数跌穿了120日线，市场避险情绪上升。外部因子看海峡—高油价—通胀—降息预期传导链。内部问题是市场风偏下降后个股普遍回调，配置型资金出现年度亏损。\\n   👍4633 💬271 🔁92\\n\\n**🔹 马靖昊**（财税专家）\\n   07:01 佰维存储2025年报：营收113亿（+69%），净利润8.5亿（暴增429%）。但现金流净额-19.65亿，经营现金流与净利润严重背离，需警惕。\\n   👍158 💬25 🔁110\\n\\n**🔹 李大霄**（前券商首席经济学家）\\n   09:48 余钱好股不悲观之五\\n   21:54 余钱好股不悲观之四\\n   共10条微博，今日主要围绕\\\"余钱好股不悲观\\\"系列\\n\\n**🔹 投行泰山**（财经博主）\\n   14:26 沪深300ETF在放量买入了，可能是国家队在维稳了\\n   14:11 全球市场再次开启无差别抛售模式，黄金正在从避险资产变为抛售对象\\n\\n**🔹 杨德龙**（前海开源基金首席经济学家）\\n   12:29 不要把投资想的太复杂，成功的投资者是把简单做到极致。——本杰明·格雷厄姆\\n   21:24 发布头条文章：《杨德龙：2026年资本市场的投资主线》\\n\\n**🔹 麒炜投资**（财经博主）\\n   11:00 大盘连续下探，很多人心态崩了。投资不是比谁赚得快，是比谁活得久。恐慌杀跌最容易把浮亏变实亏。大跌从来都是给长线投资者送低价筹码！\\n   👍28 💬4 🔁1\\n\\n── 今日要闻 ──\\n高频词：#股  #投资  #美股  #A股  #大盘\\n\\n⚠️ 仅供参考，不构成投资建议。\\n\\\" 2>&1 | tail -5\",\"timeout\":30}}],\"api\":\"anthropic-messages\",\"provider\":\"minimax-portal\",\"model\":\"MiniMax-M2.7\",\"usage\":{\"input\":109943,\"output\":880,\"cacheRead\":33079,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":143902,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1774256131418}}\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/agents/coding-agent/sessions/3b39d38b-6200-4753-bb36-e6142ae6bdb0.jsonl.reset.2026-03-28T00-39-16.800Z:27:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"7b94d818\",\"parentId\":\"9aa0812c\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-27T00:18:36.892Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"call_jnRuGlVJnrFIOcRzc6rmkWiS|fc_089fe5756451fee80169c5ccda92ec819a88b567ef31f96a62\",\"toolName\":\"read\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"#!/usr/bin/env python3\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nTrendRadar 格式化推送 V2 - 彭博/华尔街见闻风格\\n只筛选财经相关新闻，按类别分组，用专业格式推送到飞书\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nimport json, re, sys, html\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\nfrom datetime import datetime\\n\\nFEISHU_WEBHOOK = \\\"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v2/hook/f54d31a7-226d-4fac-aeaf-44b84c5c85b7\\\"\\n\\n# 严格筛选 - 只保留财经相关关键词\\nFINANCIAL_KEYWORDS = [\\n    # 市场\\n    \\\"股\\\", \\\"A股\\\", \\\"上证\\\", \\\"深证\\\", \\\"创业板\\\", \\\"科创板\\\", \\\"北证\\\", \\\"大盘\\\", \\\"指数\\\",\\n    \\\"涨\\\", \\\"跌\\\", \\\"涨停\\\", \\\"跌停\\\", \\\"牛市\\\", \\\"熊市\\\", \\\"回调\\\", \\\"反弹\\\", \\\"突破\\\",\\n    \\\"两市\\\", \\\"成交\\\", \\\"放量\\\", \\\"缩量\\\", \\\"净流入\\\", \\\"净流出\\\",\\n    # 宏观\\n    \\\"美联储\\\", \\\"降息\\\", \\\"加息\\\", \\\"CPI\\\", \\\"PPI\\\", \\\"GDP\\\", \\\"央行\\\", \\\"货币政策\\\",\\n    \\\"人民币\\\", \\\"美元\\\", \\\"汇率\\\", \\\"美债\\\", \\\"国债\\\", \\\"通胀\\\", \\\"衰退\\\", \\\"非农\\\", \\\"就业\\\",\\n    # 地缘\\n    \\\"中美\\\", \\\"关税\\\", \\\"贸易战\\\", \\\"制裁\\\", \\\"俄乌\\\", \\\"中东\\\", \\\"伊朗\\\", \\\"以色列\\\", \\\"油价\\\", \\\"原油\\\",\\n    \\\"战争\\\", \\\"冲突\\\", \\\"特朗普\\\", \\\"普京\\\",\\n    # 行业\\n    \\\"板块\\\", \\\"概念\\\", \\\"龙头\\\", \\\"主力\\\", \\\"资金\\\", \\\"热点\\\", \\\"轮动\\\", \\\"ETF\\\", \\\"外资\\\", \\\"北向\\\",\\n    # 商品\\n    \\\"黄金\\\", \\\"白银\\\", \\\"铜\\\", \\\"铝\\\", \\\"天然气\\\", \\\"大宗商品\\\",\\n    # 公司\\n    \\\"业绩\\\", \\\"财报\\\", \\\"营收\\\", \\\"利润\\\", \\\"分红\\\", \\\"回购\\\", \\\"增持\\\", \\\"减持\\\", \\\"预盈\\\", \\\"预亏\\\",\\n    # 科技\\n    \\\"AI\\\", \\\"人工智能\\\", \\\"芯片\\\", \\\"半导体\\\", \\\"英伟达\\\", \\\"算力\\\",\\n]\\n\\n# 分类关键词（互斥，只匹配一个分类）\\nCATEGORY_MAP = [\\n    (\\\"🌐 地缘政治\\\", [\\\"战争\\\", \\\"冲突\\\", \\\"制裁\\\", \\\"中东\\\", \\\"伊朗\\\", \\\"以色列\\\", \\\"中美\\\", \\\"俄乌\\\", \\\"俄罗斯\\\", \\\"普京\\\", \\\"关税\\\", \\\"贸易战\\\", \\\"北约\\\", \\\"胡塞\\\", \\\"导弹\\\", \\\"美以\\\", \\\"伊朗核\\\"]),\\n    (\\\"📊 宏观经济\\\", [\\\"美联储\\\", \\\"降息\\\", \\\"加息\\\", \\\"CPI\\\", \\\"PPI\\\", \\\"GDP\\\", \\\"央行\\\", \\\"货币政策\\\", \\\"通胀\\\", \\\"衰退\\\", \\\"非农\\\", \\\"就业\\\", \\\"财政\\\"]),\\n    (\\\"💹 A股市场\\\", [\\\"A股\\\", \\\"上证\\\", \\\"深证\\\", \\\"创业板\\\", \\\"科创板\\\", \\\"北证\\\", \\\"大盘\\\", \\\"指数\\\", \\\"涨\\\", \\\"跌\\\", \\\"涨停\\\", \\\"跌停\\\", \\\"牛市\\\", \\\"熊市\\\", \\\"回调\\\", \\\"反弹\\\", \\\"两市\\\", \\\"成交额\\\"]),\\n    (\\\"🏭 板块资金\\\", [\\\"板块\\\", \\\"概念\\\", \\\"龙头\\\", \\\"主力\\\", \\\"资金\\\", \\\"净流入\\\", \\\"净流出\\\", \\\"热点\\\", \\\"轮动\\\", \\\"ETF\\\", \\\"外资\\\", \\\"北向\\\", \\\"融资\\\", \\\"融券\\\"]),\\n    (\\\"💰 大宗商品\\\", [\\\"黄金\\\", \\\"白银\\\", \\\"铜\\\", \\\"铝\\\", \\\"原油\\\", \\\"天然气\\\", \\\"大宗商品\\\", \\\"商品期货\\\"]),\\n    (\\\"🏢 公司财报\\\", [\\\"业绩\\\", \\\"财报\\\", \\\"营收\\\", \\\"利润\\\", \\\"分红\\\", \\\"回购\\\", \\\"增持\\\", \\\"减持\\\", \\\"预盈\\\", \\\"预亏\\\", \\\"ST\\\", \\\"退市\\\"]),\\n    (\\\"🤖 AI/科技\\\", [\\\"AI\\\", \\\"人工智能\\\", \\\"芯片\\\", \\\"半导体\\\", \\\"英伟达\\\", \\\"算力\\\", \\\"大模型\\\", \\\"科技股\\\"]),\\n]\\n\\ndef clean(text):\\n    text = re.sub(r'<[^>]+>', '', str(text))\\n    text = html.unescape(text)\\n    return text.strip()\\n\\ndef parse_txt(filepath):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"解析 TrendRadar txt 文件\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    content = Path(filepath).read_text(encoding='utf-8')\\n    items = []\\n    current_source = None\\n    for line in content.split('\\\\n'):\\n        line = line.strip()\\n        if not line:\\n            continue\\n        # 源行\\n        if ' | ' in line and not line.startswith('http') and not re.match(r'^\\\\d+\\\\.', line):\\n            parts = line.split(' | ')\\n            if len(parts) == 2:\\n                current_source = parts[0].strip()\\n                continue\\n        # 新闻条目行\\n        if current_source:\\n            match = re.match(r'^\\\\d+\\\\.\\\\s+(.+?)\\\\s+\\\\[URL:(.+?)\\\\]$', line)\\n            if match:\\n                title = clean(match.group(1))\\n                url = match.group(2)\\n                items.append({'title': title, 'url': url, 'source': current_source})\\n    return items\\n\\ndef is_financial(item):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"判断是否是财经相关新闻\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    title = item['title']\\n    count = sum(1 for kw in FINANCIAL_KEYWORDS if kw in title)\\n    return count >= 1\\n\\ndef classify(item):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"给新闻分类\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    title = item['title']\\n    for cat_name, keywords in CATEGORY_MAP:\\n        for kw in keywords:\\n            if kw in title:\\n                return cat_name\\n    return None\\n\\ndef market_signal(title):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"判断市场信号\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    down = ['跌', '熊市', '回调', '利空', '大跌', '创新低', '缩量下跌', '净流出', '倒']\\n    up = ['涨', '牛市', '反弹', '利好', '大涨', '创新高', '放量上涨', '净流入', '升']\\n    t = title.lower()\\n    for w in down:\\n        if w in title: return '🔴'\\n    for w in up:\\n        if w in title: return '🟢'\\n    return '⚪'\\n\\ndef build_report(items, date_str):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"构建彭博风格报告\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    # 过滤只保留财经\\n    fin_items = [i for i in items if is_financial(i)]\\n    \\n    if not fin_items:\\n        return None\\n    \\n    # 按分类整理\\n    categories = {}\\n    for item in fin_items:\\n        cat = classify(item) or \\\"📰 其他\\\"\\n        if cat not in categories:\\n            categories[cat] = []\\n        categories[cat].append(item)\\n    \\n    # 构建消息\\n    lines = []\\n    lines.append(\\\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\")\\n    lines.append(f\\\"📡 财经热点晨报 | {date_str}\\\")\\n    lines.append(f\\\"📊 共筛选 {len(fin_items)} 条财经要闻\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\")\\n    \\n    # 按优先级输出分类\\n    for cat_name, _ in CATEGORY_MAP:\\n        cat_items = categories.get(cat_name, [])\\n        if not cat_items:\\n            continue\\n        lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n        lines.append(f\\\"{cat_name} ({len(cat_items)} 条)\\\")\\n        lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n        for item in cat_items[:6]:  # 每类最多6条\\n            signal = market_signal(item['title'])\\n            title = item['title'][:48] + ('…' if len(item['title']) > 48 else '')\\n            lines.append(f\\\"  {signal} {title}\\\")\\n    \\n    # 其他财经\\n    other = categories.get(\\\"📰 其他\\\", [])\\n    if other:\\n        lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n        lines.append(f\\\"📰 其他财经 ({len(other)} 条)\\\")\\n        lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n        for item in other[:4]:\\n            title = item['title'][:48] + ('…' if len(item['title']) > 48 else '')\\n            lines.append(f\\\"  ⚪ {title}\\\")\\n    \\n    lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\")\\n    lines.append(f\\\"📊 数据来源：TrendRadar | {datetime.now().strftime('%H:%M:%S')}\\\")\\n    \\n    return '\\\\n'.join(lines)\\n\\ndef send_feishu(text):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"发送飞书\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    import requests\\n    payload = {\\\"msg_type\\\": \\\"text\\\", \\\"content\\\": {\\\"text\\\": text}}\\n    resp = requests.post(FEISHU_WEBHOOK, json=payload, timeout=10)\\n    return resp.json()\\n\\ndef main():\\n    today = datetime.now().strftime('%Y年%m月%d日')\\n    txt_dir = Path(f\\\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/other_projects/TrendRadar/output/{today}/txt\\\")\\n    \\n    if not txt_dir.exists():\\n        print(f\\\"未找到目录: {txt_dir}\\\")\\n        sys.exit(1)\\n    \\n    txt_files = sorted(txt_dir.glob(\\\"*.txt\\\"), key=lambda p: p.stat().st_mtime, reverse=True)\\n    if not txt_files:\\n        print(\\\"未找到 txt 文件\\\")\\n        sys.exit(1)\\n    \\n    latest = txt_files[0]\\n    print(f\\\"读取: {latest.name}\\\")\\n    \\n    items = parse_txt(latest)\\n    print(f\\\"共 {len(items)} 条新闻\\\")\\n    \\n    fin_count = sum(1 for i in items if is_financial(i))\\n    print(f\\\"财经相关: {fin_count} 条\\\")\\n    \\n    date_str = datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')\\n    report = build_report(items, date_str)\\n    \\n    if report:\\n        print(\\\"\\\\n发送飞书...\\\")\\n        result = send_feishu(report)\\n        print(f\\\"结果: {result}\\\")\\n    else:\\n        print(\\\"无财经内容，跳过发送\\\")\\n\\nif __name__ == \\\"__main__\\\":\\n    main()\\n\"}],\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1774570716890}}\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/agents/coding-agent/sessions/3b39d38b-6200-4753-bb36-e6142ae6bdb0.jsonl.reset.2026-03-28T00-39-16.800Z:32:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"31054132\",\"parentId\":\"20441934\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-27T00:20:38.714Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"**Implementing title normalization**\\n\\nI’m thinking of a function called `normalize_title(title)`. First, I’d normalize using NFKC, then clean the HTML, convert to lowercase, and replace synonyms from a mapping. I want to eliminate common noise words, punctuation, and unnecessary whitespace. Maybe removing certain filler markers would help, but I’m worried about over-merging. A two-pass approach could work, where I first deduplicate exact matches, and then use similarity metrics to find near-duplicates, selecting the longer title.\\n\\n**Handling title comparisons**\\n\\nI’m considering how to manage comparisons like \\\"伊朗已正式回应美国提出的停火协议\\\" versus \\\"...15点内容.\\\" The strategy is to identify instances where the shorter title is contained within the longer one. If the sequence length ratio is around 0.76, that might indicate a match. This could help streamline the normalization process and ensure that I’m aligning similar titles effectively. I need to be careful with edge cases and make sure I’m not misgrouping titles.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_089fe5756451fee80169c5cd01352c819a95216ff0cc307456\\\"