, but I’m worried about over-merging. A two-pass approach could work, where I first deduplicate exact matches, and then use similarity metrics to find near-duplicates, selecting the longer title.\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"summary_text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"**Handling title comparisons**\\\\n\\\\nI’m considering how to manage comparisons like \\\\\\\"伊朗已正式回应美国提出的停火协议\\\\\\\" versus \\\\\\\"...15点内容.\\\\\\\" The strategy is to identify instances where the shorter title is contained within the longer one. If the sequence length ratio is around 0.76, that might indicate a match. This could help streamline the normalization process and ensure that I’m aligning similar titles effectively. I need to be careful with edge cases and make sure I’m not misgrouping titles.\\\"}]}\"},{\"type\":\"toolCall\",\"id\":\"call_J03uzt1w8CdGMtmmW7MPtdva|fc_089fe5756451fee80169c5cd0e73c8819a8610b960aab2afdb\",\"name\":\"write\",\"arguments\":{\"file_path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/other_projects/TrendRadar/format_push_v2.py\",\"content\":\"#!/usr/bin/env python3\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\nTrendRadar 格式化推送 V2 - 彭博/华尔街见闻风格\\n只筛选财经相关新闻，按类别分组，用专业格式推送到飞书\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nfrom __future__ import annotations\\n\\nimport html\\nimport json\\nimport os\\nimport re\\nimport sys\\nimport unicodedata\\nfrom datetime import datetime\\nfrom difflib import SequenceMatcher\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\nfrom typing import Dict, List, Tuple\\n\\nFEISHU_WEBHOOK = os.getenv(\\n    \\\"FEISHU_WEBHOOK\\\",\\n    \\\"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v2/hook/f54d31a7-226d-4fac-aeaf-44b84c5c85b7\\\",\\n)\\n\\n# 严格筛选 - 只保留财经相关关键词\\nFINANCIAL_KEYWORDS = [\\n    # 市场\\n    \\\"股\\\",\\n    \\\"A股\\\",\\n    \\\"上证\\\",\\n    \\\"深证\\\",\\n    \\\"创业板\\\",\\n    \\\"科创板\\\",\\n    \\\"北证\\\",\\n    \\\"大盘\\\",\\n    \\\"指数\\\",\\n    \\\"涨\\\",\\n    \\\"跌\\\",\\n    \\\"涨停\\\",\\n    \\\"跌停\\\",\\n    \\\"牛市\\\",\\n    \\\"熊市\\\",\\n    \\\"回调\\\",\\n    \\\"反弹\\\",\\n    \\\"突破\\\",\\n    \\\"两市\\\",\\n    \\\"成交\\\",\\n    \\\"放量\\\",\\n    \\\"缩量\\\",\\n    \\\"净流入\\\",\\n    \\\"净流出\\\",\\n    # 宏观\\n    \\\"美联储\\\",\\n    \\\"降息\\\",\\n    \\\"加息\\\",\\n    \\\"CPI\\\",\\n    \\\"PPI\\\",\\n    \\\"GDP\\\",\\n    \\\"央行\\\",\\n    \\\"货币政策\\\",\\n    \\\"人民币\\\",\\n    \\\"美元\\\",\\n    \\\"汇率\\\",\\n    \\\"美债\\\",\\n    \\\"国债\\\",\\n    \\\"通胀\\\",\\n    \\\"衰退\\\",\\n    \\\"非农\\\",\\n    \\\"就业\\\",\\n    # 地缘\\n    \\\"中美\\\",\\n    \\\"关税\\\",\\n    \\\"贸易战\\\",\\n    \\\"制裁\\\",\\n    \\\"俄乌\\\",\\n    \\\"中东\\\",\\n    \\\"伊朗\\\",\\n    \\\"以色列\\\",\\n    \\\"油价\\\",\\n    \\\"原油\\\",\\n    \\\"战争\\\",\\n    \\\"冲突\\\",\\n    \\\"特朗普\\\",\\n    \\\"普京\\\",\\n    # 行业\\n    \\\"板块\\\",\\n    \\\"概念\\\",\\n    \\\"龙头\\\",\\n    \\\"主力\\\",\\n    \\\"资金\\\",\\n    \\\"热点\\\",\\n    \\\"轮动\\\",\\n    \\\"ETF\\\",\\n    \\\"外资\\\",\\n    \\\"北向\\\",\\n    # 商品\\n    \\\"黄金\\\",\\n    \\\"白银\\\",\\n    \\\"铜\\\",\\n    \\\"铝\\\",\\n    \\\"天然气\\\",\\n    \\\"大宗商品\\\",\\n    # 公司\\n    \\\"业绩\\\",\\n    \\\"财报\\\",\\n    \\\"营收\\\",\\n    \\\"利润\\\",\\n    \\\"分红\\\",\\n    \\\"回购\\\",\\n    \\\"增持\\\",\\n    \\\"减持\\\",\\n    \\\"预盈\\\",\\n    \\\"预亏\\\",\\n    # 科技\\n    \\\"AI\\\",\\n    \\\"人工智能\\\",\\n    \\\"芯片\\\",\\n    \\\"半导体\\\",\\n    \\\"英伟达\\\",\\n    \\\"算力\\\",\\n]\\n\\n# 分类关键词（互斥，只匹配一个分类）\\nCATEGORY_MAP = [\\n    (\\n        \\\"🌐 地缘政治\\\",\\n        [\\n            \\\"战争\\\",\\n            \\\"冲突\\\",\\n            \\\"制裁\\\",\\n            \\\"中东\\\",\\n            \\\"伊朗\\\",\\n            \\\"以色列\\\",\\n            \\\"中美\\\",\\n            \\\"俄乌\\\",\\n            \\\"俄罗斯\\\",\\n            \\\"普京\\\",\\n            \\\"关税\\\",\\n            \\\"贸易战\\\",\\n            \\\"北约\\\",\\n            \\\"胡塞\\\",\\n            \\\"导弹\\\",\\n            \\\"美以\\\",\\n            \\\"伊朗核\\\",\\n        ],\\n    ),\\n    (\\\"📊 宏观经济\\\", [\\\"美联储\\\", \\\"降息\\\", \\\"加息\\\", \\\"CPI\\\", \\\"PPI\\\", \\\"GDP\\\", \\\"央行\\\", \\\"货币政策\\\", \\\"通胀\\\", \\\"衰退\\\", \\\"非农\\\", \\\"就业\\\", \\\"财政\\\"]),\\n    (\\\"💹 A股市场\\\", [\\\"A股\\\", \\\"上证\\\", \\\"深证\\\", \\\"创业板\\\", \\\"科创板\\\", \\\"北证\\\", \\\"大盘\\\", \\\"指数\\\", \\\"涨\\\", \\\"跌\\\", \\\"涨停\\\", \\\"跌停\\\", \\\"牛市\\\", \\\"熊市\\\", \\\"回调\\\", \\\"反弹\\\", \\\"两市\\\", \\\"成交额\\\"]),\\n    (\\\"🏭 板块资金\\\", [\\\"板块\\\", \\\"概念\\\", \\\"龙头\\\", \\\"主力\\\", \\\"资金\\\", \\\"净流入\\\", \\\"净流出\\\", \\\"热点\\\", \\\"轮动\\\", \\\"ETF\\\", \\\"外资\\\", \\\"北向\\\", \\\"融资\\\", \\\"融券\\\"]),\\n    (\\\"💰 大宗商品\\\", [\\\"黄金\\\", \\\"白银\\\", \\\"铜\\\", \\\"铝\\\", \\\"原油\\\", \\\"天然气\\\", \\\"大宗商品\\\", \\\"商品期货\\\"]),\\n    (\\\"🏢 公司财报\\\", [\\\"业绩\\\", \\\"财报\\\", \\\"营收\\\", \\\"利润\\\", \\\"分红\\\", \\\"回购\\\", \\\"增持\\\", \\\"减持\\\", \\\"预盈\\\", \\\"预亏\\\", \\\"ST\\\", \\\"退市\\\"]),\\n    (\\\"🤖 AI/科技\\\", [\\\"AI\\\", \\\"人工智能\\\", \\\"芯片\\\", \\\"半导体\\\", \\\"英伟达\\\", \\\"算力\\\", \\\"大模型\\\", \\\"科技股\\\"]),\\n]\\n\\nSYNONYM_PATTERNS: Tuple[Tuple[str, str], ...] = (\\n    (r\\\"美国\\\", \\\"美\\\"),\\n    (r\\\"中国\\\", \\\"中\\\"),\\n    (r\\\"英国\\\", \\\"英\\\"),\\n    (r\\\"欧盟\\\", \\\"欧\\\"),\\n    (r\\\"(15)\\\\s*点\\\\s*内容\\\", r\\\"\\\\1点\\\"),\\n    (r\\\"(\\\\d+)\\\\s*点\\\\s*停火协议\\\", r\\\"\\\\1点停火协议\\\"),\\n    (r\\\"(\\\\d+)\\\\s*点\\\\s*停火提议\\\", r\\\"\\\\1点停火提议\\\"),\\n    (r\\\"伊斯兰革命卫队\\\", \\\"革命卫队\\\"),\\n)\\n\\nNOISE_PATTERNS: Tuple[str, ...] = (\\n    r\\\"^【[^】]+】\\\",\\n    r\\\"^\\\\[[^\\\\]]+\\\\]\\\",\\n    r\\\"^画面来了[!！:：]?\\\",\\n    r\\\"^深夜[^：:]*[:：]\\\",\\n    r\\\"^快讯[!！:：]?\\\",\\n    r\\\"^突发[!！:：]?\\\",\\n)\\n\\n\\ndef clean(text: str) -> str:\\n    text = re.sub(r\\\"<[^>]+>\\\", \\\"\\\", str(text))\\n    text = html.unescape(text)\\n    return text.strip()\\n\\n\\n\\ndef parse_txt(filepath: Path) -> List[Dict[str, str]]:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"解析 TrendRadar txt 文件\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    content = Path(filepath).read_text(encoding=\\\"utf-8\\\")\\n    items: List[Dict[str, str]] = []\\n    current_source = None\\n    for line in content.split(\\\"\\\\n\\\"):\\n        line = line.strip()\\n        if not line:\\n            continue\\n        # 源行\\n        if \\\" | \\\" in line and not line.startswith(\\\"http\\\") and not re.match(r\\\"^\\\\d+\\\\.\\\", line):\\n            parts = line.split(\\\" | \\\")\\n            if len(parts) == 2:\\n                current_source = parts[0].strip()\\n                continue\\n        # 新闻条目行\\n        if current_source:\\n            match = re.match(r\\\"^\\\\d+\\\\.\\\\s+(.+?)\\\\s+\\\\[URL:(.+?)\\\\]$\\\", line)\\n            if match:\\n                title = clean(match.group(1))\\n                url = match.group(2)\\n                items.append({\\\"title\\\": title, \\\"url\\\": url, \\\"source\\\": current_source})\\n    return items\\n\\n\\n\\ndef is_financial(item: Dict[str, str]) -> bool:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"判断是否是财经相关新闻\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    title = item[\\\"title\\\"]\\n    count = sum(1 for kw in FINANCIAL_KEYWORDS if kw in title)\\n    return count >= 1\\n\\n\\n\\ndef classify(item: Dict[str, str]) -> str | None:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"给新闻分类\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    title = item[\\\"title\\\"]\\n    for cat_name, keywords in CATEGORY_MAP:\\n        for kw in keywords:\\n            if kw in title:\\n                return cat_name\\n    return None\\n\\n\\n\\ndef market_signal(title: str) -> str:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"判断市场信号\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    down = [\\\"跌\\\", \\\"熊市\\\", \\\"回调\\\", \\\"利空\\\", \\\"大跌\\\", \\\"创新低\\\", \\\"缩量下跌\\\", \\\"净流出\\\", \\\"倒\\\"]\\n    up = [\\\"涨\\\", \\\"牛市\\\", \\\"反弹\\\", \\\"利好\\\", \\\"大涨\\\", \\\"创新高\\\", \\\"放量上涨\\\", \\\"净流入\\\", \\\"升\\\"]\\n    for word in down:\\n        if word in title:\\n            return \\\"🔴\\\"\\n    for word in up:\\n        if word in title:\\n            return \\\"🟢\\\"\\n    return \\\"⚪\\\"\\n\\n\\n\\ndef normalize_title(title: str) -> str:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Normalize titles for exact and near-duplicate detection.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    normalized = unicodedata.normalize(\\\"NFKC\\\", clean(title)).lower()\\n\\n    for pattern in NOISE_PATTERNS:\\n        normalized = re.sub(pattern, \\\"\\\", normalized)\\n\\n    for pattern, replacement in SYNONYM_PATTERNS:\\n        normalized = re.sub(pattern, replacement, normalized)\\n\\n    normalized = normalized.replace(\\\"“\\\", \\\"\\\").replace(\\\"”\\\", \\\"\\\")\\n    normalized = normalized.replace(\\\"‘\\\", \\\"\\\").replace(\\\"’\\\", \\\"\\\")\\n    normalized = re.sub(r\\\"[\\\\s\\\\-—–_:：;；,，.。!！?？'\\\\\\\"`()\\\\[\\\\]{}<>《》/\\\\\\\\|]+\\\", \\\"\\\", normalized)\\n    return normalized.strip()\\n\\n\\n\\ndef title_similarity(left: str, right: str) -> float:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Return similarity score between two normalized titles.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    if not left or not right:\\n        return 0.0\\n    if left == right:\\n        return 1.0\\n    return SequenceMatcher(None, left, right).ratio()\\n\\n\\n\\ndef choose_better_item(current: Dict[str, str], candidate: Dict[str, str]) -> Dict[str, str]:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Prefer the more informative title when merging duplicates.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    current_title = current[\\\"title\\\"]\\n    candidate_title = candidate[\\\"title\\\"]\\n\\n    current_score = (len(current_title), len(current.get(\\\"url\\\", \\\"\\\")))\\n    candidate_score = (len(candidate_title), len(candidate.get(\\\"url\\\", \\\"\\\")))\\n    return candidate if candidate_score > current_score else current\\n\\n\\n\\ndef is_near_duplicate(normalized: str, existing_normalized: str) -> bool:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Conservative near-duplicate detection for same-event title variants.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    if not normalized or not existing_normalized:\\n        return False\\n\\n    shorter, longer = sorted((normalized, existing_normalized), key=len)\\n    similarity = title_similarity(normalized, existing_normalized)\\n\\n    if shorter and shorter in longer and len(shorter) / max(len(longer), 1) >= 0.7:\\n        return True\\n\\n    return similarity >= 0.93\\n\\n\\n\\ndef deduplicate_items(items: List[Dict[str, str]]) -> Tuple[List[Dict[str, str]], int]:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Remove exact and near-duplicate headlines.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    deduplicated: List[Dict[str, str]] = []\\n    normalized_keys: List[str] = []\\n\\n    for item in items:\\n        normalized = normalize_title(item[\\\"title\\\"])\\n        duplicate_index = None\\n\\n        for index, existing_normalized in enumerate(normalized_keys):\\n            if normalized == existing_normalized or is_near_duplicate(normalized, existing_normalized):\\n                duplicate_index = index\\n                break\\n\\n        if duplicate_index is None:\\n            deduplicated.append(item)\\n            normalized_keys.append(normalized)\\n            continue\\n\\n        best_item = choose_better_item(deduplicated[duplicate_index], item)\\n        deduplicated[duplicate_index] = best_item\\n        normalized_keys[duplicate_index] = normalize_title(best_item[\\\"title\\\"])\\n\\n    removed = len(items) - len(deduplicated)\\n    return deduplicated, removed\\n\\n\\n\\ndef build_report(items: List[Dict[str, str]], date_str: str) -> str | None:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"构建彭博风格报告\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    fin_items = [item for item in items if is_financial(item)]\\n    if not fin_items:\\n        return None\\n\\n    deduped_items, duplicates_removed = deduplicate_items(fin_items)\\n    if not deduped_items:\\n        return None\\n\\n    categories: Dict[str, List[Dict[str, str]]] = {}\\n    for item in deduped_items:\\n        category = classify(item) or \\\"📰 其他\\\"\\n        categories.setdefault(category, []).append(item)\\n\\n    lines: List[str] = []\\n    lines.append(\\\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\")\\n    lines.append(f\\\"📡 财经热点晨报 | {date_str}\\\")\\n    lines.append(f\\\"📊 原始财经 {len(fin_items)} 条｜去重后 {len(deduped_items)} 条\\\")\\n    if duplicates_removed:\\n        lines.append(f\\\"🧹 已筛除重复 {duplicates_removed} 条\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\")\\n\\n    for cat_name, _ in CATEGORY_MAP:\\n        cat_items = categories.get(cat_name, [])\\n        if not cat_items:\\n            continue\\n        lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n        lines.append(f\\\"{cat_name} ({len(cat_items)} 条)\\\")\\n        lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n        for item in cat_items[:6]:\\n            signal = market_signal(item[\\\"title\\\"])\\n            title = item[\\\"title\\\"][:48] + (\\\"…\\\" if len(item[\\\"title\\\"]) > 48 else \\\"\\\")\\n            lines.append(f\\\"  {signal} {title}\\\")\\n\\n    other_items = categories.get(\\\"📰 其他\\\", [])\\n    if other_items:\\n        lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n        lines.append(f\\\"📰 其他财经 ({len(other_items)} 条)\\\")\\n        lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n        for item in other_items[:4]:\\n            title = item[\\\"title\\\"][:48] + (\\\"…\\\" if len(item[\\\"title\\\"]) > 48 else \\\"\\\")\\n            lines.append(f\\\"  ⚪ {title}\\\")\\n\\n    lines.append(\\\"\\\")\\n    lines.append(\\\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\")\\n    lines.append(f\\\"📊 数据来源：TrendRadar | {datetime.now().strftime('%H:%M:%S')}\\\")\\n    return \\\"\\\\n\\\".join(lines)\\n\\n\\n\\ndef send_feishu(text: str) -> dict:\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"发送飞书\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    import requests\\n\\n    payload = {\\\"msg_type\\\": \\\"text\\\", \\\"content\\\": {\\\"text\\\": text}}\\n    response = requests.post(FEISHU_WEBHOOK, json=payload, timeout=10)\\n    return response.json()\\n\\n\\n\\ndef main() -> None:\\n    today = datetime.now().strftime(\\\"%Y年%m月%d日\\\")\\n    txt_dir = Path(f\\\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/other_projects/TrendRadar/output/{today}/txt\\\")\\n\\n    if not txt_dir.exists():\\n        print(f\\\"未找到目录: {txt_dir}\\\")\\n        sys.exit(1)\\n\\n    txt_files = sorted(txt_dir.glob(\\\"*.txt\\\"), key=lambda path: path.stat().st_mtime, reverse=True)\\n    if not txt_files:\\n        print(\\\"未找到 txt 文件\\\")\\n        sys.exit(1)\\n\\n    latest = txt_files[0]\\n    print(f\\\"读取: {latest.name}\\\")\\n\\n    items = parse_txt(latest)\\n    print(f\\\"共 {len(items)} 条新闻\\\")\\n\\n    financial_items = [item for item in items if is_financial(item)]\\n    deduped_items, duplicates_removed = deduplicate_items(financial_items)\\n    print(f\\\"财经相关: {len(financial_items)} 条\\\")\\n    print(f\\\"去重后: {len(deduped_items)} 条（移除 {duplicates_removed} 条重复）\\\")\\n\\n    date_str = datetime.now().strftime(\\\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\\\")\\n    report = build_report(items, date_str)\\n\\n    if report:\\n        print(\\\"\\\\n发送飞书...\\\")\\n        result = send_feishu(report)\\n        print(f\\\"结果: {json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False)}\\\")\\n    else:\\n        print(\\\"无财经内容，跳过发送\\\")\\n\\n\\nif __name__ == \\\"__main__\\\":\\n    main()\\n\"},\"partialJson\":\"{\\\"file_path\\\":\\\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/other_projects/TrendRadar/format_push_v2.py\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"#!/usr/bin/env python3\\\\n\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\nTrendRadar 格式化推送 V2 - 彭博/华尔街见闻风格\\\\n只筛选财经相关新闻，按类别分组，用专业格式推送到飞书\\\\n\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\nfrom __future__ import annotations\\\\n\\\\nimport html\\\\nimport json\\\\nimport os\\\\nimport re\\\\nimport sys\\\\nimport unicodedata\\\\nfrom datetime import datetime\\\\nfrom difflib import SequenceMatcher\\\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\\\nfrom typing import Dict, List, Tuple\\\\n\\\\nFEISHU_WEBHOOK = os.getenv(\\\\n    \\\\\\\"FEISHU_WEBHOOK\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v2/hook/f54d31a7-226d-4fac-aeaf-44b84c5c85b7\\\\\\\",\\\\n)\\\\n\\\\n# 严格筛选 - 只保留财经相关关键词\\\\nFINANCIAL_KEYWORDS = [\\\\n    # 市场\\\\n    \\\\\\\"股\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"A股\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"上证\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"深证\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"创业板\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"科创板\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"北证\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"大盘\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"指数\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"涨\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"跌\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"涨停\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"跌停\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"牛市\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"熊市\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"回调\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"反弹\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"突破\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"两市\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"成交\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"放量\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"缩量\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"净流入\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"净流出\\\\\\\",\\\\n    # 宏观\\\\n    \\\\\\\"美联储\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"降息\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"加息\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"CPI\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"PPI\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"GDP\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"央行\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"货币政策\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"人民币\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"美元\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"汇率\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"美债\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"国债\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"通胀\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"衰退\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"非农\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"就业\\\\\\\",\\\\n    # 地缘\\\\n    \\\\\\\"中美\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"关税\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"贸易战\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"制裁\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"俄乌\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"中东\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"伊朗\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"以色列\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"油价\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"原油\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"战争\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"冲突\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"特朗普\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"普京\\\\\\\",\\\\n    # 行业\\\\n    \\\\\\\"板块\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"概念\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"龙头\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"主力\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"资金\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"热点\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"轮动\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"ETF\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"外资\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"北向\\\\\\\",\\\\n    # 商品\\\\n    \\\\\\\"黄金\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"白银\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"铜\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"铝\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"天然气\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"大宗商品\\\\\\\",\\\\n    # 公司\\\\n    \\\\\\\"业绩\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"财报\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"营收\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"利润\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"分红\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"回购\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"增持\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"减持\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"预盈\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"预亏\\\\\\\",\\\\n    # 科技\\\\n    \\\\\\\"AI\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"人工智能\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"芯片\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"半导体\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"英伟达\\\\\\\",\\\\n    \\\\\\\"算力\\\\\\\",\\\\n]\\\\n\\\\n# 分类关键词（互斥，只匹配一个分类）\\\\nCATEGORY_MAP = [\\\\n    (\\\\n        \\\\\\\"🌐 地缘政治\\\\\\\",\\\\n        [\\\\n            \\\\\\\"战争\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"冲突\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"制裁\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"中东\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"伊朗\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"以色列\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"中美\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"俄乌\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"俄罗斯\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"普京\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"关税\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"贸易战\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"北约\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"胡塞\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"导弹\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"美以\\\\\\\",\\\\n            \\\\\\\"伊朗核\\\\\\\",\\\\n        ],\\\\n    ),\\\\n    (\\\\\\\"📊 宏观经济\\\\\\\", [\\\\\\\"美联储\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"降息\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"加息\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"CPI\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"PPI\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"GDP\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"央行\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"货币政策\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"通胀\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"衰退\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"非农\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"就业\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"财政\\\\\\\"]),\\\\n    (\\\\\\\"💹 A股市场\\\\\\\", [\\\\\\\"A股\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"上证\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"深证\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"创业板\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"科创板\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"北证\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"大盘\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"指数\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"涨\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"跌\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"涨停\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"跌停\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"牛市\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"熊市\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"回调\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"反弹\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"两市\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"成交额\\\\\\\"]),\\\\n    (\\\\\\\"🏭 板块资金\\\\\\\", [\\\\\\\"板块\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"概念\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"龙头\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"主力\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"资金\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"净流入\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"净流出\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"热点\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"轮动\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"ETF\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"外资\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"北向\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"融资\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"融券\\\\\\\"]),\\\\n    (\\\\\\\"💰 大宗商品\\\\\\\", [\\\\\\\"黄金\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"白银\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"铜\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"铝\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"原油\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"天然气\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"大宗商品\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"商品期货\\\\\\\"]),\\\\n    (\\\\\\\"🏢 公司财报\\\\\\\", [\\\\\\\"业绩\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"财报\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"营收\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"利润\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"分红\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"回购\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"增持\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"减持\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"预盈\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"预亏\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"ST\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"退市\\\\\\\"]),\\\\n    (\\\\\\\"🤖 AI/科技\\\\\\\", [\\\\\\\"AI\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"人工智能\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"芯片\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"半导体\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"英伟达\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"算力\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"大模型\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"科技股\\\\\\\"]),\\\\n]\\\\n\\\\nSYNONYM_PATTERNS: Tuple[Tuple[str, str], ...] = (\\\\n    (r\\\\\\\"美国\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"美\\\\\\\"),\\\\n    (r\\\\\\\"中国\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"中\\\\\\\"),\\\\n    (r\\\\\\\"英国\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"英\\\\\\\"),\\\\n    (r\\\\\\\"欧盟\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"欧\\\\\\\"),\\\\n    (r\\\\\\\"(15)\\\\\\\\s*点\\\\\\\\s*内容\\\\\\\", r\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\1点\\\\\\\"),\\\\n    (r\\\\\\\"(\\\\\\\\d+)\\\\\\\\s*点\\\\\\\\s*停火协议\\\\\\\", r\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\1点停火协议\\\\\\\"),\\\\n    (r\\\\\\\"(\\\\\\\\d+)\\\\\\\\s*点\\\\\\\\s*停火提议\\\\\\\", r\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\1点停火提议\\\\\\\"),\\\\n    (r\\\\\\\"伊斯兰革命卫队\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"革命卫队\\\\\\\"),\\\\n)\\\\n\\\\nNOISE_PATTERNS: Tuple[str, ...] = (\\\\n    r\\\\\\\"^【[^】]+】\\\\\\\",\\\\n    r\\\\\\\"^\\\\\\\\[[^\\\\\\\\]]+\\\\\\\\]\\\\\\\",\\\\n    r\\\\\\\"^画面来了[!！:：]?\\\\\\\",\\\\n    r\\\\\\\"^深夜[^：:]*[:：]\\\\\\\",\\\\n    r\\\\\\\"^快讯[!！:：]?\\\\\\\",\\\\n    r\\\\\\\"^突发[!！:：]?\\\\\\\",\\\\n)\\\\n\\\\n\\\\ndef clean(text: str) -> str:\\\\n    text = re.sub(r\\\\\\\"<[^>]+>\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\", str(text))\\\\n    text = html.unescape(text)\\\\n    return text.strip()\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\ndef parse_txt(filepath: Path) -> List[Dict[str, str]]:\\\\n    \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"解析 TrendRadar txt 文件\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    content = Path(filepath).read_text(encoding=\\\\\\\"utf-8\\\\\\\")\\\\n    items: List[Dict[str, str]] = []\\\\n    current_source = None\\\\n    for line in content.split(\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\"):\\\\n        line = line.strip()\\\\n        if not line:\\\\n            continue\\\\n        # 源行\\\\n        if \\\\\\\" | \\\\\\\" in line and not line.startswith(\\\\\\\"http\\\\\\\") and not re.match(r\\\\\\\"^\\\\\\\\d+\\\\\\\\.\\\\\\\", line):\\\\n            parts = line.split(\\\\\\\" | \\\\\\\")\\\\n            if len(parts) == 2:\\\\n                current_source = parts[0].strip()\\\\n                continue\\\\n        # 新闻条目行\\\\n        if current_source:\\\\n            match = re.match(r\\\\\\\"^\\\\\\\\d+\\\\\\\\.\\\\\\\\s+(.+?)\\\\\\\\s+\\\\\\\\[URL:(.+?)\\\\\\\\]$\\\\\\\", line)\\\\n            if match:\\\\n                title = clean(match.group(1))\\\\n                url = match.group(2)\\\\n                items.append({\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\": title, \\\\\\\"url\\\\\\\": url, \\\\\\\"source\\\\\\\": current_source})\\\\n    return items\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\ndef is_financial(item: Dict[str, str]) -> bool:\\\\n    \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"判断是否是财经相关新闻\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    title = item[\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\"]\\\\n    count = sum(1 for kw in FINANCIAL_KEYWORDS if kw in title)\\\\n    return count >= 1\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\ndef classify(item: Dict[str, str]) -> str | None:\\\\n    \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"给新闻分类\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    title = item[\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\"]\\\\n    for cat_name, keywords in CATEGORY_MAP:\\\\n        for kw in keywords:\\\\n            if kw in title:\\\\n                return cat_name\\\\n    return None\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\ndef market_signal(title: str) -> str:\\\\n    \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"判断市场信号\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    down = [\\\\\\\"跌\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"熊市\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"回调\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"利空\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"大跌\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"创新低\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"缩量下跌\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"净流出\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"倒\\\\\\\"]\\\\n    up = [\\\\\\\"涨\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"牛市\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"反弹\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"利好\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"大涨\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"创新高\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"放量上涨\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"净流入\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"升\\\\\\\"]\\\\n    for word in down:\\\\n        if word in title:\\\\n            return \\\\\\\"🔴\\\\\\\"\\\\n    for word in up:\\\\n        if word in title:\\\\n            return \\\\\\\"🟢\\\\\\\"\\\\n    return \\\\\\\"⚪\\\\\\\"\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\ndef normalize_title(title: str) -> str:\\\\n    \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"Normalize titles for exact and near-duplicate detection.\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    normalized = unicodedata.normalize(\\\\\\\"NFKC\\\\\\\", clean(title)).lower()\\\\n\\\\n    for pattern in NOISE_PATTERNS:\\\\n        normalized = re.sub(pattern, \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\", normalized)\\\\n\\\\n    for pattern, replacement in SYNONYM_PATTERNS:\\\\n        normalized = re.sub(pattern, replacement, normalized)\\\\n\\\\n    normalized = normalized.replace(\\\\\\\"“\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\").replace(\\\\\\\"”\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\")\\\\n    normalized = normalized.replace(\\\\\\\"‘\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\").replace(\\\\\\\"’\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\")\\\\n    normalized = re.sub(r\\\\\\\"[\\\\\\\\s\\\\\\\\-—–_:：;；,，.。!！?？'\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"`()\\\\\\\\[\\\\\\\\]{}<>《》/\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\|]+\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\", normalized)\\\\n    return normalized.strip()\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\ndef title_similarity(left: str, right: str) -> float:\\\\n    \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"Return similarity score between two normalized titles.\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    if not left or not right:\\\\n        return 0.0\\\\n    if left == right:\\\\n        return 1.0\\\\n    return SequenceMatcher(None, left, right).ratio()\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\ndef choose_better_item(current: Dict[str, str], candidate: Dict[str, str]) -> Dict[str, str]:\\\\n    \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"Prefer the more informative title when merging duplicates.\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    current_title = current[\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\"]\\\\n    candidate_title = candidate[\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\"]\\\\n\\\\n    current_score = (len(current_title), len(current.get(\\\\\\\"url\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\")))\\\\n    candidate_score = (len(candidate_title), len(candidate.get(\\\\\\\"url\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\")))\\\\n    return candidate if candidate_score > current_score else current\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\ndef is_near_duplicate(normalized: str, existing_normalized: str) -> bool:\\\\n    \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"Conservative near-duplicate detection for same-event title variants.\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    if not normalized or not existing_normalized:\\\\n        return False\\\\n\\\\n    shorter, longer = sorted((normalized, existing_normalized), key=len)\\\\n    similarity = title_similarity(normalized, existing_normalized)\\\\n\\\\n    if shorter and shorter in longer and len(shorter) / max(len(longer), 1) >= 0.7:\\\\n        return True\\\\n\\\\n    return similarity >= 0.93\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\ndef deduplicate_items(items: List[Dict[str, str]]) -> Tuple[List[Dict[str, str]], int]:\\\\n    \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"Remove exact and near-duplicate headlines.\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    deduplicated: List[Dict[str, str]] = []\\\\n    normalized_keys: List[str] = []\\\\n\\\\n    for item in items:\\\\n        normalized = normalize_title(item[\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\"])\\\\n        duplicate_index = None\\\\n\\\\n        for index, existing_normalized in enumerate(normalized_keys):\\\\n            if normalized == existing_normalized or is_near_duplicate(normalized, existing_normalized):\\\\n                duplicate_index = index\\\\n                break\\\\n\\\\n        if duplicate_index is None:\\\\n            deduplicated.append(item)\\\\n            normalized_keys.append(normalized)\\\\n            continue\\\\n\\\\n        best_item = choose_better_item(deduplicated[duplicate_index], item)\\\\n        deduplicated[duplicate_index] = best_item\\\\n        normalized_keys[duplicate_index] = normalize_title(best_item[\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\"])\\\\n\\\\n    removed = len(items) - len(deduplicated)\\\\n    return deduplicated, removed\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\ndef build_report(items: List[Dict[str, str]], date_str: str) -> str | None:\\\\n    \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"构建彭博风格报告\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    fin_items = [item for item in items if is_financial(item)]\\\\n    if not fin_items:\\\\n        return None\\\\n\\\\n    deduped_items, duplicates_removed = deduplicate_items(fin_items)\\\\n    if not deduped_items:\\\\n        return None\\\\n\\\\n    categories: Dict[str, List[Dict[str, str]]] = {}\\\\n    for item in deduped_items:\\\\n        category = classify(item) or \\\\\\\"📰 其他\\\\\\\"\\\\n        categories.setdefault(category, []).append(item)\\\\n\\\\n    lines: List[str] = []\\\\n    lines.append(\\\\\\\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\\\\")\\\\n    lines.append(f\\\\\\\"📡 财经热点晨报 | {date_str}\\\\\\\")\\\\n    lines.append(f\\\\\\\"📊 原始财经 {len(fin_items)} 条｜去重后 {len(deduped_items)} 条\\\\\\\")\\\\n    if duplicates_removed:\\\\n        lines.append(f\\\\\\\"🧹 已筛除重复 {duplicates_removed} 条\\\\\\\")\\\\n    lines.append(\\\\\\\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\\\\")\\\\n\\\\n    for cat_name, _ in CATEGORY_MAP:\\\\n        cat_items = categories.get(cat_name, [])\\\\n        if not cat_items:\\\\n            continue\\\\n        lines.append(\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\")\\\\n        lines.append(f\\\\\\\"{cat_name} ({len(cat_items)} 条)\\\\\\\")\\\\n        lines.append(\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\")\\\\n        for item in cat_items[:6]:\\\\n            signal = market_signal(item[\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\"])\\\\n            title = item[\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\"][:48] + (\\\\\\\"…\\\\\\\" if len(item[\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\"]) > 48 else \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\")\\\\n            lines.append(f\\\\\\\"  {signal} {title}\\\\\\\")\\\\n\\\\n    other_items = categories.get(\\\\\\\"📰 其他\\\\\\\", [])\\\\n    if other_items:\\\\n        lines.append(\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\")\\\\n        lines.append(f\\\\\\\"📰 其他财经 ({len(other_items)} 条)\\\\\\\")\\\\n        lines.append(\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\")\\\\n        for item in other_items[:4]:\\\\n            title = item[\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\"][:48] + (\\\\\\\"…\\\\\\\" if len(item[\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\"]) > 48 else \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\")\\\\n            lines.append(f\\\\\\\"  ⚪ {title}\\\\\\\")\\\\n\\\\n    lines.append(\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\")\\\\n    lines.append(\\\\\\\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\\\\\\")\\\\n    lines.append(f\\\\\\\"📊 数据来源：TrendRadar | {datetime.now().strftime('%H:%M:%S')}\\\\\\\")\\\\n    return \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\".join(lines)\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\ndef send_feishu(text: str) -> dict:\\\\n    \\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"发送飞书\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\"\\\\n    import requests\\\\n\\\\n    payload = {\\\\\\\"msg_type\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\": {\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\": text}}\\\\n    response = requests.post(FEISHU_WEBHOOK, json=payload, timeout=10)\\\\n    return response.json()\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\ndef main() -> None:\\\\n    today = datetime.now().strftime(\\\\\\\"%Y年%m月%d日\\\\\\\")\\\\n    txt_dir = Path(f\\\\\\\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/other_projects/TrendRadar/output/{today}/txt\\\\\\\")\\\\n\\\\n    if not txt_dir.exists():\\\\n        print(f\\\\\\\"未找到目录: {txt_dir}\\\\\\\")\\\\n        sys.exit(1)\\\\n\\\\n    txt_files = sorted(txt_dir.glob(\\\\\\\"*.txt\\\\\\\"), key=lambda path: path.stat().st_mtime, reverse=True)\\\\n    if not txt_files:\\\\n        print(\\\\\\\"未找到 txt 文件\\\\\\\")\\\\n        sys.exit(1)\\\\n\\\\n    latest = txt_files[0]\\\\n    print(f\\\\\\\"读取: {latest.name}\\\\\\\")\\\\n\\\\n    items = parse_txt(latest)\\\\n    print(f\\\\\\\"共 {len(items)} 条新闻\\\\\\\")\\\\n\\\\n    financial_items = [item for item in items if is_financial(item)]\\\\n    deduped_items, duplicates_removed = deduplicate_items(financial_items)\\\\n    print(f\\\\\\\"财经相关: {len(financial_items)} 条\\\\\\\")\\\\n    print(f\\\\\\\"去重后: {len(deduped_items)} 条（移除 {duplicates_removed} 条重复）\\\\\\\")\\\\n\\\\n    date_str = datetime.now().strftime(\\\\\\\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\\\\\\\")\\\\n    report = build_report(items, date_str)\\\\n\\\\n    if report:\\\\n        print(\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n发送飞书...\\\\\\\")\\\\n        result = send_feishu(report)\\\\n        print(f\\\\\\\"结果: {json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False)}\\\\\\\")\\\\n    else:\\\\n        print(\\\\\\\"无财经内容，跳过发送\\\\\\\")\\\\n\\\\n\\\\nif __name__ == \\\\\\\"__main__\\\\\\\":\\\\n    main()\\\\n\\\"}\"}],\"api\":\"openai-responses\",\"provider\":\"codex\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.4\",\"usage\":{\"input\":849,\"output\":4731,\"cacheRead\":45696,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":51276,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"toolUse\",\"timestamp\":1774570749524,\"responseId\":\"resp_089fe5756451fee80169c5ccff16fc819a98f42ad37c026b2e\"}}\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/agents/coding-agent/sessions/ecdf003a-7e1d-4d2b-910e-70972d6c037f.jsonl.reset.2026-03-31T22-34-49.377Z:276:{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"9fe58046\",\"parentId\":\"338f6831\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-31T12:32:22.393Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"message_id\\\": \\\"om_x100b538fa2373538c4d863da01bc3ce\\\",\\n  \\\"reply_to_id\\\": \\\"om_x100b538f3aac2884c357ab91c7f7a5d\\\",\\n  \\\"sender_id\\\": \\\"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\\\",\\n  \\\"conversation_label\\\": \\\"oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\\\",\\n  \\\"sender\\\": \\\"张玲\\\",\\n  \\\"timestamp\\\": \\\"Tue 2026-03-31 20:32 GMT+8\\\",\\n  \\\"group_subject\\\": \\\"oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\\\",\\n  \\\"is_group_chat\\\": true,\\n  \\\"was_mentioned\\\": true,\\n  \\\"has_reply_context\\\": true\\n}\\n```\\n\\nSender (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"label\\\": \\\"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\\\",\\n  \\\"id\\\": \\\"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\\\",\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"张玲\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"body\\\": \\\"📊 微博财经大V每日简报\\\\n🕐 2026\\\\\\\\-03\\\\\\\\-31 20:00  \\\\\\\\|  共 10 位大V  \\\\\\\\|  财经内容 0 条\\\\n── 重点内容摘录 ──\\\\n── 今日要闻 ──\\\\n⚠️ 仅供参考，不构成投资建议。\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n[message